subject: America's Cup
Sailboats and Sailing
lead_paragraph: The American entry BMW Oracle Racing preserved its unbeaten streak in the Louis Vuitton Cup yacht racing series by defeating the Italian syndicate Luna Rossa Tuesday in the fifth flight.
